## Intro

Welcome to Jabber Jazz | Fan-driven, Ad-free content on Utah Jazz basketball

Adam Bushman [Twitter | @adam_bushman](https://www.twitter.com/adam_bushman)

Today:

*   Our third look ahead to the 2023 NBA draft

Guest:

*   Mark [@MarkW_E01](https://twitter.com/MarkW_E01)
    -   Jazz and Falcons super fan
    -   Long history of NBA & NFL draft analysis


Like what we're doing? Consider...

*   Subscribing
*   Following
*   Leaving a review or comment
*   Snagging some merch

Let's Jabber Jazz!


## Third 2023 NBA draft Look Ahead

Starter Questions:

*   What matters/doesn't matter to you different from consensus in prospect evaluation?
*   What are the player archtypes or skills that "break ties" for you?
*   What's the next fad you anticipate that defines player comps and skill set preferences?



::: {.cell}

:::


